   The services that CAP provides the following Services,
     * Search-and-Rescue
     * Disaster Relief
     * Emergency Communications
     * Aerial Imaging
     * Counter-Drug Program

   A new national emergency services curriculum is in the process of being
   developed to insure that our members adhere to a single unified
   standard. Search-and-Rescue At the Air Force's direction, CAP flies 85
   percent or more of the inland air search-and-rescue missions in the
   United States each year. A New CAPF 108 is now available for Download!

